{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It's great being here at TED."},{"time":3000,"text":"You know, I think there might be some presentations"},{"time":5000,"text":"that will go over my head,"},{"time":7000,"text":"but the most amazing concepts"},{"time":9000,"text":"are the ones that go right under my feet."},{"time":12000,"text":"The little things in life,"},{"time":14000,"text":"sometimes that we forget about,"},{"time":16000,"text":"like pollination, that we take for granted."},{"time":19000,"text":"And you can't tell the story about pollinators --"},{"time":22000,"text":"bees, bats, hummingbirds, butterflies --"},{"time":25000,"text":"without telling the story about the invention of flowers"},{"time":28000,"text":"and how they co-evolved"},{"time":30000,"text":"over 50 million years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"I've been filming time-lapse flowers"},{"time":34000,"text":"24 hours a day, seven days a week,"},{"time":37000,"text":"for over 35 years."},{"time":39000,"text":"To watch them move"},{"time":41000,"text":"is a dance I'm never going to get tired of."},{"time":43000,"text":"It fills me with wonder, and it opens my heart."},{"time":47000,"text":"Beauty and seduction, I believe,"},{"time":49000,"text":"is nature's tool for survival,"},{"time":52000,"text":"because we will protect what we fall in love with."},{"time":55000,"text":"Their relationship"},{"time":57000,"text":"is a love story that feeds the Earth."},{"time":60000,"text":"It reminds us that we are a part of nature,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and we're not separate from it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"When I heard about the vanishing bees, Colony Collapse Disorder,"},{"time":69000,"text":"it motivated me to take action."},{"time":71000,"text":"We depend on pollinators"},{"time":73000,"text":"for over a third of the fruits and vegetables we eat."},{"time":77000,"text":"And many scientists believe"},{"time":79000,"text":"it's the most serious issue facing mankind."},{"time":82000,"text":"It's like the canary in the coalmine."},{"time":84000,"text":"If they disappear, so do we."},{"time":87000,"text":"It reminds us that we are a part of nature"},{"time":89000,"text":"and we need to take care of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"What motivated me to film their behavior"},{"time":96000,"text":"was something that I asked my scientific advisers:"},{"time":99000,"text":"\"What motivates the pollinators?\""},{"time":102000,"text":"Well, their answer was,"},{"time":104000,"text":"\"It's all about risk and reward.\""},{"time":107000,"text":"Like a wide-eyed kid, I'd say, \"Why is that?\""},{"time":110000,"text":"And they'd say, \"Well, because they want to survive.\""},{"time":112000,"text":"I go, \"Why?\""},{"time":114000,"text":"\"Well, in order to reproduce.\""},{"time":116000,"text":"\"Well, why?\""},{"time":118000,"text":"And I thought that they'd probably say, \"Well, it's all about sex.\""},{"time":122000,"text":"And Chip Taylor, our monarch butterfly expert,"},{"time":125000,"text":"he replied, \"Nothing lasts forever."},{"time":129000,"text":"Everything in the universe wears out.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"And that blew my mind."},{"time":133000,"text":"Because I realized"},{"time":135000,"text":"that nature had invented reproduction"},{"time":137000,"text":"as a mechanism for life to move forward,"},{"time":140000,"text":"as a life force that passes right through us"},{"time":144000,"text":"and makes us a link in the evolution of life."},{"time":148000,"text":"Rarely seen by the naked eye,"},{"time":150000,"text":"this intersection"},{"time":152000,"text":"between the animal world and the plant world"},{"time":154000,"text":"is truly a magic moment."},{"time":156000,"text":"It's the mystical moment"},{"time":158000,"text":"where life regenerates itself,"},{"time":160000,"text":"over and over again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"So here is some nectar from my film."},{"time":166000,"text":"I hope you'll drink, tweet"},{"time":168000,"text":"and plant some seeds"},{"time":170000,"text":"to pollinate a friendly garden."},{"time":172000,"text":"And always take time to smell the flowers,"},{"time":175000,"text":"and let it fill you with beauty,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and rediscover that sense of wonder."},{"time":180000,"text":"Here are some images from the film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":437000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}